<plot>Scars Don't Sweat is a down and dirty look at the 1998 racing season of Gunnar Shogren, an East Coast mountain biking legend. At 36 years of age, and over a decade of racing under his belt, Gunnar is facing the end of his racing career, and more importantly, the end of a way of life. Scars Don't Sweat attempts to capture this emotional struggle of a professional athlete facing the end of his career - when is it time to move on?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?479878</url></doc>
